          acceptedAnswer: { '@type': 'Answer', text: 'Angel Bail Bonds offers competitive rates on Kay County bail bonds. The exact premium depends on the bail amount set by the court. We accept cash, Visa, Mastercard, Zelle, and Venmo, and offer financing options for larger bonds. Call (405) 614-3000 for a free quote on your specific situation.' },
        },
